===============
Process catalog
===============

Processes are sorted by the following categories:

    * upload
    * import
    * analyses
    * analyses:alignment
    * analyses:variants
    * jbrowse
    * uncategorized

List of processes is quite long, you can navigate or search them in the menu bar on the left.
